A doodle inspired by RPGs and hexagonal games. The controls are:

                  forward

                     W
    forward-left  Q     E  forward-right
       back-left  A     D  back-right
                     S

                  backward

Building requires `glm`, `SDL2`, `SDL_image`, `OpenGL`, and a working POSIX
build system:

    make && ./postpile

